{{DISPLAYTITLE:A_FireMacePL2}}
'''A_FireMacePL2'''<br>
(''no parameter'')<br>

Fires a {{Class|MaceFX4}} and plays the sound "weapons/maceshoot" on the WEAPON channel. The player's horizontal velocities are added to the ball's owns, so that player momentum is transferred to the projectile. The ball's vertical velocity is greater by two points than dictated by the player's pitch, through clamped between +7 and -3. If the player has a possible target straight ahead, this target is put in the ball's <tt>tracer</tt> field.

This codepointer is restricted to {{Class|MacePowered}} and derived classes.

